                            <comment id="217694" author="utopiabound" created="Mon, 8 Jan 2018 16:11:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This looks like it fails because for DNE each MDT is waited for serially in &lt;tt&gt;sanity-scrub.sh::scrub_check_status()&lt;/tt&gt;, thus if one of the middle MDTs takes a long time (test log shows &quot;Waiting 6 secs for update&quot;) then the end ones may complete before being able to show up as &quot;scanning&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
